spfft
------------------------------------------
A 3D FFT library for sparse frequency domain data written in C++ with support
for MPI, OpenMP, CUDA and ROCm.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.5-1
  libfftw3-devel-3.3.10-1
  libfftw3_3-3.3.10-1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libgomp1-11.3.0-1
  libopenmpi40-4.1.2-1
  libspfft-devel-1.0.6-1bl1
  libspfft1-1.0.6-1bl1
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1
  pkg-config-1.8.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.38-1
  cmake-3.20.0-1
  cygport-0.35.1-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-fortran-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libfftw3-devel-3.3.10-1
  libopenmpi-devel-4.1.2-1
  make-4.3-1
  ninja-1.11.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/eth-cscs/spfft

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/eth-cscs/spfft/archive/refs/tags/v1.0.6.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack spfft-1.0.6-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./spfft-1.0.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/spfft-1.0.6-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/spfft-1.0.6-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libspfft1-1.0.6-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libspfft-devel-1.0.6-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

